---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="AI Transparency" description="How I use AI tools on this website.">
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">AI Transparency</h1>

    <div class="prose mt-10">
      <p>
        If you use AI professionally and write about it, you should be upfront about how you do it. This is my attempt.
      </p>

      <h2>What I use AI for</h2>
      <p>
        I use language models as tools: for research, structuring, writing, and programming. This website and its content are created with AI assistance. Ideas, direction, and accountability are mine.
      </p>

      <h2>What stays with me</h2>
      <p>
        The decision about what gets published. Every post is reviewed, understood, and approved by me. The opinions are mine.
      </p>

      <h2>Accountability</h2>
      <p>
        Mistakes on this site are my mistakes. Tools don't change that.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
